tag_management.description_hr: Kategorija za upravljanje oznakama, omogućuje kreiranje, brisanje, dohvaćanje i ažuriranje oznaka.
tag_management.description_en: Category for managing tags, allowing for the creation, deletion, retrieval, and updating of tags.

trip_management.name: trip_management
trip_management.description_hr: Kategorija za upravljanje putovanjima omogućuje korisnicima dodavanje, ažuriranje i brisanje putničkih podataka.
trip_management.description_en: The trip management category allows users to add, update, and delete travel data.

trip_document_management.name: trip_document_management
trip_document_management.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje upravljanje dokumentima vezanim uz putovanja. Korisnici mogu dodavati, preuzimati, ažurirati i brisati dokumente vezane uz određene putove.
trip_document_management.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows for the management of documents related to trips. Users can add, retrieve, update, and delete documents associated with specific trips.

trip_metadata.name: trip_metadata
trip_metadata.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje pristup metapodacima putovanja. Korisnici mogu dobiti detaljne informacije o specifičnim entitetima povezanima s putovanjima.
trip_metadata.description_en: This category of API endpoints provides access to trip metadata. Users can retrieve detailed information about specific entities related to trips.

trip_data_projection.name: trip_data_projection
trip_data_projection.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje korisnicima da dobiju sve stavke na temelju parametara učitavanja (lazy) za projiciranje podataka o putovanjima.
trip_data_projection.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows users to retrieve all items based on load parameters (lazy) for projecting trip data.

trip_data_aggregation.name: trip_data_aggregation
trip_data_aggregation.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje agregaciju podataka o putovanjima, pružajući korisnicima mogućnost dobivanja sažetka informacija na temelju različitih funkcija agregacije.
trip_data_aggregation.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows for the aggregation of trip data, providing users with the ability to retrieve summarized information based on various aggregate functions.

trip_data_grouping.name: trip_data_grouping
trip_data_grouping.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje grupiranje podataka o putovanjima prema različitim kriterijima.
trip_data_grouping.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows for the grouping of trip data based on various criteria.

trip_type_management.name: trip_type_management
trip_type_management.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje upravljanje tipovima putovanja, uključujući kreiranje, brisanje, dohvaćanje i ažuriranje podataka o tipovima putovanja.
trip_type_management.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows for the management of trip types, including creating, deleting, retrieving, and updating trip type data.

trip_type_document_management.name: trip_type_document_management
trip_type_document_management.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje upravljanje dokumentima vezanim uz tipove putovanja, uključujući dodavanje, ažuriranje i brisanje dokumenata.
trip_type_document_management.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows for the management of documents related to trip types, including adding, updating, and deleting documents.
typical_intents: Retrieve documents for a trip type
Update a specific document for a trip type

trip_type_metadata.name: trip_type_metadata
trip_type_metadata.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje pristup metapodacima o različitim tipovima putovanja.
trip_type_metadata.description_en: This category of API endpoints provides access to metadata about different trip types.

trip_type_data_projection.name: trip_type_data_projection
trip_type_data_projection.description_hr: Ova kategorija omogućuje pristup podacima o vrstama putovanja temeljenim na parametrima učitavanja.
trip_type_data_projection.description_en: This category provides access to trip type data based on load parameters.

trip_type_data_aggregation.name: trip_type_data_aggregation
trip_type_data_aggregation.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje agregaciju podataka o vrstama putovanja. Korisnici mogu dobiti vrijednosti prema specificiranim agregatnim funkcijama.
trip_type_data_aggregation.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows for the aggregation of trip type data. Users can retrieve values based on specified aggregate functions.

trip_type_data_grouping.name: trip_type_data_grouping
trip_type_data_grouping.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje grupiranje podataka o vrstama putovanja za analizu i izvještavanje.
trip_type_data_grouping.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows for the grouping of trip type data for analysis and reporting.

vehicle_board_management.name: vehicle_board_management
vehicle_board_management.description_hr: Kategorija API endpointa za upravljanje podacima o vozilima na ploči. Omogućuje pristup informacijama o vozilima i njihovom statusu.
vehicle_board_management.description_en: API endpoint category for managing vehicle board data. It provides access to information about vehicles and their status.

vehicle_calendar_management.name: vehicle_calendar_management
vehicle_calendar_management.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje upravljanje kalendarom vozila, uključujući kreiranje, brisanje i ažuriranje unosa.
vehicle_calendar_management.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows for the management of vehicle calendars, including creating, deleting, and updating entries.

vehicle_calendar_document_management.name: vehicle_calendar_document_management
vehicle_calendar_document_management.description_hr: Upravljanje dokumentima vezanim uz vozila i kalendare. Ovaj API omogućuje dodavanje, ažuriranje i brisanje dokumenata povezanih s vozilima.
vehicle_calendar_document_management.description_en: Management of documents related to vehicles and calendars. This API allows for adding, updating, and deleting documents associated with vehicles.

contract_management.name: contract_management
contract_management.description_hr: Upravlja ugovorima vezanim uz vozila, omogućujući dodavanje, brisanje i ažuriranje ugovora.
contract_management.description_en: Manages vehicle-related contracts, allowing for the addition, deletion, and updating of contracts.

input_helper.name: input_helper
input_helper.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa pruža pomoć pri unosu podataka vezanih uz vozila, uključujući marke, modele i prethodne vozila.
input_helper.description_en: This category of API endpoints provides assistance in data input related to vehicles, including brands, models, and previous vehicles.

external_data.name: external_data
external_data.description_hr: Ova kategorija omogućuje pristup vanjskim podacima vezanim uz vozila, uključujući informacije iz drugih aplikacija.
external_data.description_en: This category provides access to external data related to vehicles, including information from other applications.

assignment_management.name: assignment_management
assignment_management.description_hr: Kategorija koja upravlja dodjelama vozila, omogućujući pregled i filtriranje informacija o dodjelama na temelju različitih parametara.
assignment_management.description_en: A category that manages vehicle assignments, allowing for the overview and filtering of assignment information based on various parameters.

historical_data_management.name: historical_data_management
historical_data_management.description_hr: Upravlja povijesnim podacima vozila, omogućujući kreiranje, brisanje, dohvaćanje i ažuriranje unosa podataka.
historical_data_management.description_en: Manages historical vehicle data, allowing for the creation, deletion, retrieval, and updating of data entries.

historical_data_info.name: historical_data_info
historical_data_info.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa pruža informacije o povijesnim podacima vezanim uz vozila. Korisnici mogu dobiti metapodatke o određenim entitetima.
historical_data_info.description_en: This category of API endpoints provides information about historical data related to vehicles. Users can retrieve metadata for specific entities.

vehicle_type_management.name: vehicle_type_management
vehicle_type_management.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje upravljanje vrstama vozila, uključujući kreiranje, brisanje, dohvaćanje i ažuriranje podataka o vozilima.
vehicle_type_management.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows for the management of vehicle types, including creating, deleting, retrieving, and updating vehicle data.

metadata_retrieval.name: metadata_retrieval
metadata_retrieval.description_hr: Ova kategorija API endpointa omogućuje dohvaćanje metapodataka za različite entitete. Korisnici mogu pristupiti specifičnim informacijama o vozilima i drugim objektima.
metadata_retrieval.description_en: This category of API endpoints allows for the retrieval of metadata for various entities. Users can access specific information about vehicles and other objects.
